          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> plant based</strong> <strong>'Nduja </strong>and the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4 or more? Use 2 pans!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
