            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> with 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[275ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>and<strong> half </strong>your <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Bring to the boil, then cook for 5-6 min or until the sauce has thickened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1722495159861-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1722495159861-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1722495159861-x700.jpg",
